UA=Name of your main nation.
PASSWORD=Password of your nation.
EMAIL=cluthcybears@wp.pl
TARGET_REGION=The List
TARGET_REGION_PASSWORD=poopet
PRETITLE=New pretitle of the nation. Max length of 28. Nation must have minimum population of 250 million.
SLOGAN=New Slogan/Motto of the nation. Max length of 55.
CURRENCY=New currency of the nation. Min length of 2.  Max length of 40.
ANIMAL=New national animal of the nation. Min length of 2. Max length of 40.
DEMONYM_NOUN=Noun the nation will refer to its citizens as. Min length of 2. Max length of 44.
DEMONYM_ADJECTIVE=Adjective the nation will refer to its citizens as. Min length of 2. Max length of 44.
DEMONYM_PLURAL=Plural form of "demonym_noun". Min length of 2. Max length of 44.
FLAG=File name of your flag like flag.png